18:38.117 --> 18:40.095
I don't know
what's wrong with me.

18:40.119 --> 18:41.597
You're probably just tired.

18:41.621 --> 18:44.270
My mom and I heard you
up all night.

18:44.294 --> 18:47.204
It just keeps
coming out too thick.

18:50.129 --> 18:52.107
You know,
people aren't gonna care

18:52.131 --> 18:54.680
if the icing isn't perfect.

18:54.704 --> 18:59.285
People care about details.

18:59.309 --> 19:01.587
Someday when Danielle
looks back,

19:01.611 --> 19:04.690
I want her to remember
just how perfect her cake looked

19:04.714 --> 19:07.601
and how hard her mother worked
to make her happy.

